-- Saudi Prince Alwaleed mulls Kuwait's Zain buy: report
-- 
-- Sun Mar 13, 2011 1:22am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/13/us-alwaleed-zain-idUSTRE72C0NC20110313

 

 KUWAIT  (Reuters) - Saudi billionaire Prince Alwaleed bin Talal is considering to buy a controlling stake in Kuwaiti telecom firm Zain ( ZAIN.KW ) at a price of 1.7 dinars ($6.12) per share, a newspaper reported on Sunday. 

 "Saudi businessman Alwaleed bin Talal is currently considering to submit an offer to buy a controlling stake in Zain," Kuwaiti daily newspaper al-Seyassah said in an unsourced report. (Reporting by Eman Goma; Editing by Shaheen Pasha)